claim.claim-text:
1. A method of fabricating a damage sensor, comprising the steps of:
applying a predetermined strain to an NiTi-alloy film;
soaking the strain-applied NiTi-alloy film with an acidic aqueous solution to remove an oxide film that has coated the NiTi-alloy film;
coating the oxide film-removed NiTi-film with a protective film; and
bonding a film of an electric circuit with strain gages to the protective film-coated NiTi-film.
